  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Capacity building of employers&apos; organizations in Uruguay</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims at strengthening the capacity of employers&#x2019; organizations in Uruguay to promote an enabling environment for sustainable enterprises in the country and to provide additional services to its members. The project has two components: 1) development of a business service in the Chamber of Industries of Uruguay (CIU) using ILO&#x2019;s SOLVE (Integrating health promotion into workplace OHS policy) methodology to improve productivity through the implementation of good safety and health at work practices; and 2) support to CIU and the Chamber of Commerce and Services of Uruguay to enable them to develop policy proposals for productive development, using the tools developed by the ILO to analyse the business environment.</narrative>
  </description>
